ProjectsArray.Title: E-commerce Fragrance Website
ProjectsArray.About: An e-commerce site dedicated to perfumes and colognes, offering a unique shopping experience tailored to individual preferences. With a wide selection of fragrances categorize by notes, customers can easily explore and discover new scents based on their favorite fragrance ingredients.

ProjectsArray.Title: Appointment Scheduler
ProjectsArray.About: The Java appointment scheduler GUI is a powerful tool designed to streamline the process of scheduling appointments and managing associated users.  With its intuitive interface and comprehensive features, it offers a convenient solution for efficiently organizing and tracking appointments.

ProjectsArray.Title: Sorting Visualizer
ProjectsArray.About: The Sorting Visualizer is a web application designed to assist in visualizing sorting algorithms.  It provides a comprehensive toolset for displaying the step-by-step execution of various sorting algorithms including, Bubble Sort, Selection Sort, Insertion Sort, and Merge Sort.

ProjectsArray.Title: Parcel Delivery Service
ProjectsArray.About: The Parcel Delivery Service creates route planning and minimizes delivery time and fuel costs by implementing the greedy algorithm.  It incorporates a hash table data structure to store and access package information, making it efficient to facilitate quick and accurate package lookup based on user's input and allows users to locate individual packages at a specific time.
